Observation: This paper developed a transition model not for the population of the plant, but for a population of patches occupied by the plant. Thus the stages are not life cycle stages, the transitions do not have the same interpretations as do transitions among life cycle stages, and demographic analyses describe spatial spread, not dynamics of numbers.
checknote: The is a population spread model, life stages are not life stages!
